foia:ProcessedRequestSection.foia:FootnoteText: * In the FY2013 Annual FOIA Report, ITA reported the number of requests pending at the end of FY2013 as “43.” This number was reported incorrectly. The difference of “1” request is due to 1 request processed entirely under the Privacy Act in FY2013, but not documented until FY 2014. The correct number is “42.” Therefore, the number of requests pending as of the start of FY2014 for ITA has been amended to “42” in the FY2014 Annual FOIA Report.

**In the FY2013 Annual FOIA Report, NOAA reported the number of requests pending at the end of FY2013 as “139.” This number was reported incorrectly. The difference of “11” requests is due to 11 requests pending from FY 2013 but not reported, which were fulfilled in FY 2014. The correct number is “150.” Therefore, the number of requests pending as of the start of FY2014 for NOAA has been amended to “150” in the FY2014 Annual FOIA Report.

*** In the FY2013 Annual FOIA Report, OIG reported the number of requests pending at the end of FY2013 as “4.” This number was reported incorrectly. The difference of “1” request is due to requests fulfilled in FY2013, but not documented until FY 2014. The correct number is “3.” Therefore, the number of requests pending as of the start of FY2014 for NOAA has been amended to “3” in the FY2014 Annual FOIA Report.

**** In the FY2013 Annual FOIA Report, PTO reported the number of requests pending at the end of FY2013 as “24.” This number was reported incorrectly. The difference of “1” request is due to requests fulfilled in FY2013, but not documented until FY 2014. The correct number is “23.” Therefore, the number of requests pending as of the start of FY2014 for NOAA has been amended to “23” in the FY2014 Annual FOIA Report.

***** In the FY2013 Annual FOIA Report, the agency overall number of requests pending at the end of FY2013 was reported as “358.” Due to the amendment in the number of requests pending as of the start of FY2013 for ITA, NOAA and OIG (see footnotes above), the agency overall number of requests pending as of the start of FY2013 has been amended to “366.”
